HOSPITAL LIEN
Notice is hereby given that a hospital known as DELL SETON MEDICAL CENTER located at 1500 RED RIVER STREET AUSTIN TEXAS
78701 claims a lien, in accordance to Chapter 55 of the Texas Property Code, for the treatment, care and maintenance of the following
injured individual: 1
SARAH JACOBS (3114470847)
8104 TAPO LN AUSTIN, TX 78724
On or about 11/08/2021, the individual allegedw sustained personal injuries and sought treatment for said injuries within seventy-
two (72) hours as a result of the accident. Treatment, care and maintenance was provided by DELL SETON MEDICAL CENTER for a
period of no longer than one hundred days, and the amount due is based upon charges that are reasonable and at a regular rate for
such services. The name(s) of the person(s), if known, alleged to be liable for the damages arising from said injury are:
This lien will attach to any cause of action or chain the injured individual may have against another person for the individual's injuries;
and the lien does not attach to real property owned by the injured individual.
Dated 3 / 11/2022
DELL SETON MEDICAL CENTER
